Question: Which team won the most matches in 2015?
GeneratedSql:
SELECT T.team_long_name FROM Team AS T JOIN (
    SELECT home_team_api_id AS winner_team_id FROM Match WHERE home_team_goal > away_team_goal AND SUBSTR(date, 1, 4) = '2015'
    UNION ALL
    SELECT away_team_api_id AS winner_team_id FROM Match WHERE away_team_goal > home_team_goal AND SUBSTR(date, 1, 4) = '2015'
) AS Winners ON T.team_api_id = Winners.winner_team_id GROUP BY T.team_long_name ORDER BY COUNT(Winners.winner_team_id) DESC LIMIT 1

Question: Which team won the most matches in 2015?
GeneratedSql:
SELECT
  T.team_long_name
FROM (
  SELECT
    M.home_team_api_id AS team_id
  FROM Match AS M
  WHERE
    STRFTIME('%Y', M.date) = '2015' AND M.home_team_goal > M.away_team_goal
  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    M.away_team_api_id AS team_id
  FROM Match AS M
  WHERE
    STRFTIME('%Y', M.date) = '2015' AND M.away_team_goal > M.home_team_goal
) AS Wins
JOIN Team AS T
  ON Wins.team_id = T.team_api_id
GROUP BY
  T.team_long_name
ORDER BY
  COUNT(Wins.team_id) DESC
LIMIT 1;
